Package: joincheckr
Type: Package
Title: Get information for left join of two data frames
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Tobias Stalder
Maintainer: Tobias Stalder <tobias.stalder.geo@outlook.com>
Description: This package offers simple functions to get information
    on the potential result of a left join between two data frames.
	For example, calculate how many rows of x will have at
	least one join partner in y based on a common join ID.
